node.title: One person dead after truck crash in Tararua District
node.description: A person has died following a crash in Waitahora in the Tararua District.
node.content:
["A person has died following a crash in Waitahora in the Tararua District.", "", "
\nPhoto: RNZ / Tom Kitchin\n
", "Emergency services were called to Weber Road around 2.45pm, where a truck had overturned.", "Police said in a statement that one person died at the scene.", "The road was closed while the Serious Crash Unit carried out an investigation.", "It has since re-opened.", "Earlier one person died in a crash that left two others in hospital with serious injuries in Hastings District.", "Emergency services were called to the two-car crash in Pukehamoamoa, shortly before 4pm.", "The Serious Crash Unit is investigating."]
